        <h3 id="summary">Summary</h3>

        <p>
            In this article we learn't how to get unique data within collection using <Highlight>Distinct</Highlight> and <Highlight>DistinctBy</Highlight>. We also 
            learnt how to get unique object by passing an expression. All these can be used with any <Highlight>IEnumerable</Highlight> or <Highlight>IQueryable</Highlight> 
            types.
